data.text:
Summary[]

Sanjay surprises Gita. Sonia's worries unite Carol and Alan. Roy goes looking for Phil and Ben. Meanwhile Kathy calls the police to report what Phil has done. Eventually Phil is traced to the allotments where Kathy, Pat and Roy confront him. Kathy takes Ben back and returns to Pat's house determined to stop Phil seeing Ben again. Bianca wants to sell her share of Deals on Wheels to Barry so she can get more money for her wedding but Ricky talks her out of it when he realises Barry's offer of Â£3200 is too low. Phil begs Kathy to give him one more chance.
